Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.64,0:00:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗  好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.96,0:00:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.85,0:00:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.22,0:00:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前不是也很积极的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.47,0:00:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  比起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.09,0:00:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这周会去参加末车站前的庆典吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.06,0:00:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  不要岔开话题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.16,0:00:20.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你们继续加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.42,0:00:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人份
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.14,0:00:29.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下就32%了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.24,0:00:35.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一天多一点的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.65,0:00:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩下38%  情势怎么看都还很严峻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.04,0:00:43.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距学园祭复活署名裁决日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.54,0:00:45.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有34小时
